title: Foolproof Indian-Style Beef Enchiladas with Radish Salad & Yoghurt
description: A bold fusion of cuisines, this dish wraps tender Mumbai-spiced beef in crispy tortillas. Paired with a refreshing radish salad and tangy Greek yoghurt, it’s a meal that’s vibrant, fun, and oh-so-delicious. Perfect for when you’re craving something adventurous!
